    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088760/extras/89d27eeaf6e38a1a160a5183ba6ed67d.avif?t=1754594515\" width=600 height=90 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088760/extras/7aa33626112183855472cc7050c450c8.poster.avif?t=1754594515\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088760/extras/7aa33626112183855472cc7050c450c8.webm?t=1754594515\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088760/extras/7aa33626112183855472cc7050c450c8.mp4?t=1754594515\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Step into the enchanting world of <i>The Faylands</i>, a kingdom brimming with ancient magic and fantastical creatures known as Fays. As a Keeper, you possess the unique ability to control, train, and evolve these wondrous beast. Master the art of Fay Keeping, conquer all Colosseums and become the ultimate champion!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088760/extras/042cc11dd3a55fe268500a25a54126e6.avif?t=1754594515\" width=600 height=90 /></span>Discover and collect over a hundred diverse Fays. Train them, battle against other Keepers, and face wild Fays. Utilize powerful abilities like Overcharge, Drain, and Ultramorph to dominate your foes and master the world of Fay Keeping.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088760/extras/f189978247b985355abcb8ff2c070d7a.avif?t=1754594515\" width=600 height=90 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088760/extras/85479c1e70708115c7d219eef9e52ff5.poster.avif?t=1754594515\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088760/extras/85479c1e70708115c7d219eef9e52ff5.webm?t=1754594515\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088760/extras/85479c1e70708115c7d219eef9e52ff5.mp4?t=1754594515\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Engage in a complex and resource-intensive battle system. Manage your Fay’s Energy, Life, and multiple statuses to gain the upper hand. Leverage Elemental Types, Weather conditions, buffs, and debuffs to outsmart your opponents and control the battlefield.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088760/extras/3ec3df06c355fa859436754631a89101.avif?t=1754594515\" width=600 height=90 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088760/extras/51c2f4419752f326d912add822267922.poster.avif?t=1754594515\" width=600 height=148 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088760/extras/51c2f4419752f326d912add822267922.webm?t=1754594515\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088760/extras/51c2f4419752f326d912add822267922.mp4?t=1754594515\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Tap the full potential of your evolved Fays by Ultramorphing them into their ultimate forms in the heat of battle. This transformation unleashes immense power, but not without a cost that will test even the most skilled Keepers!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088760/extras/15db16c9141791fcad777edc3cac3a39.avif?t=1754594515\" width=600 height=90 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088760/extras/48e295abde9a40d52ff6bc64fa6a3a8d.poster.avif?t=1754594515\" width=600 height=104 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088760/extras/48e295abde9a40d52ff6bc64fa6a3a8d.webm?t=1754594515\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088760/extras/48e295abde9a40d52ff6bc64fa6a3a8d.mp4?t=1754594515\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Harness the power of Overdrive to amplify your Fay’s abilities. Use this potent technique to overcome the dangers lurking in the wild Faelands and defeat your enemies with enhanced strength.</p>",
